Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受引导之人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边一切都还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的,除了训练还是训练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都顺利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我们一同前来的魔导士们呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是来带迪兰度回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向被魔导士所忌讳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不清楚详情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是在嫉妒弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也讨厌魔导士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样批评魔导士喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾经担任过魔导士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是想着能够再见到您…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们真是感到抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就来为我效力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这颗心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了您而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费了好大的功夫才发现\N原来这是用幻之月的文字写的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷,拜托您就别再闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,被寨巴哈盯上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对不会有好下场的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下来要到幻之谷去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就搭这艘船回帕拉斯去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货物没了,您又不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要我怎么向老爷交代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你写张条子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要说我跟蜜拉娜公主在一起就不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会去的,因为亚连要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我得去?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是你老爸抛弃妻小\N甚至一切财产才找到的幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事在阿斯多利亚可是出了名的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连我也听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷是龙神人的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去看看我体内龙神人之血的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有它和艾斯卡弗洛尼又有着什么样的牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不晓得究竟是什么机缘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群与幻之谷有关的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水晶北东之年,绿十二之月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正朝从未有人探访过的黑暗大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯加尔德大陆前去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,幻之谷一定就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能找到自己长年追寻的"诞生奇迹之力"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,就是"亚特兰提斯之力"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了,舵根本不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种暴风雨中根本就没办法航行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长,情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能源石的温度降不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是龙神的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訑不许人类进入这片海域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿把船掉头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟当初说的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经支付你要求的酬劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去船会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也很清楚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经将自己的性命卖给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不晓得过了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朦胧之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了那名少女的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了那名少女的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯加尔德大陆\N出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是神在引导我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那年轻岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于离奇的命运所引导的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后突如其来的别离
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了确认深深刻画在我心中对那名少女的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都在幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有我所追寻的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不惜抛家弃子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是为了要找一个女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸还挺有意思的啊\N什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少强过我那个只会数钞票的老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很欣赏这种生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有任何线索吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是你们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们千万别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…现在还是会作那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会梦到自己上学前和以往一样在车站等着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后小瞳就会跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却总是只梦到那里就醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会梦到小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有遇上困难但那孩子不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面除了海还是海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续笔直前进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸说是这个方位没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的话可信吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长都说要相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能硬着头皮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派鲁,你那边情况怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:09:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要组装从德莱甸的人型装甲上\N取下来的操演宫零件挺花时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了,这颗螺丝就是栓不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,可别弄坏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青十六之月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧烈的暴风雪与惊险的岩场阻挡了我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛是在测试向谜团挑战的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也就在那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一名老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有人也跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信幻之谷的存在而旅行寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问他叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他叫艾萨克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我从未跟人提起过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过告诉你们或许比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾听家母说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也恰好是在小瞳这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在参加完夏日庆典回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她整个人突然被光芒所笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来自己已身处一个从未见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克的话相当有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也在寻找幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追寻着亚特兰提斯之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最令人惊讶的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克跟那名女孩一样说自己是从幻之月来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是家母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然会是幻之月人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了要断绝一切束缚才开始这段旅程的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你的双眸却让我觉得这一切都毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意原谅我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚德罗福斯将军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来请求您允许让迪兰度回国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔导士竟然会征询我的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说他是我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他原本就是你们这些魔导士交给我的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把理由告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到军师弗肯如此通知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只恶鬼竟然也会生病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是无奇不有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待他康复之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会再将他送至亚德罗福斯将军麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈来愈不安定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因为何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运改变实验仍有缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点得对弗肯保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歇士达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪、达雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会有危险别扔下我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先让他睡个觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回国之后再对他进行再一次的命运改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯加尔德岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们…正朝幻之谷去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯之民 龙神人的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他们给发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白三之月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与艾萨克终于抵达一片满是浓雾的原野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信幻之谷一定就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾几何时艾萨克消失了踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在这片浓雾中跟我走失了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我只要一心想着要抵达幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能解开亚特兰提斯之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必定能够再次见到那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到她之后,我将…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃走是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂的天空骑士竟然会因为\N这点小事就产生动摇,真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人真不讨人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没想过要你来喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你那么说太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又被可爱的女孩给讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小瞳吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看笑话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是无法原谅那家伙…无法原谅家父
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅抛家弃子的他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连,你不是还保韶着\N你父亲的日志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以丢掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却没有那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在心里某处\N你一定很希望能多了解他一些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没办法极度憎恶某个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你真的带有那样的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定也就不会那么爱戴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你一定很想原谅你的父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我只是在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只是不愿意去承认自己是被父亲给抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意原谅我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能通过这里,马上就会到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,你就待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:17:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连浮游石都飞了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利甸,好好看着前方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被撞上就没戏唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你们在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到掌舵室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面出现浮游石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是幻之谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺了一页
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寨巴哈的浮游要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现阿斯多利亚高速艇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅,耶莉雅,你们听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,我们随时可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会将您弟弟带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙,上方被压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把我们逼到地面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派鲁,谢拉撒特好了没?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,还不能出动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念一定能够实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要无时无刻都强烈地希望着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,这个你拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆,请让我能见到幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家都能见到幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我都要看到幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后,您究竟期望我怎么做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能在这里被击败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与父亲您做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,你究竟要到幻之谷去看什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚特兰提斯之门竟然开敔了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:57.59,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:06.04,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:13.67,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.98,0:22:19.82,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:22.18,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:27.19,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:31.03,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:34.83,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:38.84,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
